                    <p>Every model reflects the finest details of the original vehicle.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="icon-box p-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-car mb-3"></i>
                    <h5>Diverse Collection</h5>
