                <i class="fas fa-bullseye fa-2x float-start me-3"></i>
                At Unique, we aim to be the go-to platform for scale model enthusiasts worldwide, celebrating the beauty of vehicles in all their forms.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Values Section -->
        <h2 class="mt-5 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="values-box p-4">
