                    <p>Stay updated with the latest models and exclusive releases.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="values-box p-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-users fa-2x mb-3" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i>
                    <h5>Community</h5>
                    <p>Building a global network of scale model collectors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Join Our Journey Section -->
        <h2 class="mt-5 mb-4">Join Our Journey</h2>
        <p>
            Whether you're a seasoned collector or new to the world of scaled vehicles, Unique is here to fuel your passion. Explore our collection, discover rare gems, and experience the joy of miniatures brought to life.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <p class="h4 mb-4">Let's make your collection as Unique as you are!</p>
            <a href="/AboutUs" class="btn btn-unique btn-lg">Explore Our Collection</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

